{"type": "game", "name": "Soldat 2", "steam_appid": 474220, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our community on Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>The original</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474220/extras/steam_ezgif.com-gif-maker__8_.gif?t=1727253409\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soldat 2 recreates the classic experience of online deathmatch made famous by its predecessor, with the same physics-based movement, violence and guns. And much more . With a new stylized 2.5D look, ranked multiplayer, QoS improvements, customizations and new exciting weapons, maps and game modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/474220/extras/steam_ezgif.com-gif-maker__20_.gif?t=1727253409\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Can be played with bots!<br><br>For multiplayer, because the community is small<br>- it is recommended to join DISCORD and ask to play<br>- can be played with friends using Steam Friends invitations<br>- the game supports RANKED MULTIPLAYER match making (but please join Discord to see what time is best to play)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> iconic physics-based movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> online multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> ranked/gather mode with player statistics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> capture the flag, team/deathmatch, <strong>domination</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> realistic weapons and military equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> ragdoll physics and over the top violence</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> singleplayer with bots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragrap